cs.SE, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.PL, cs.AI 

The paper discusses the need for engineering long-lived software and stable architectures, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The focus is on self-adaptive cloud architectures, which involves distributed computing (cs.DC) and system-level issues (cs.SY). The proposed framework involves online learning and stochastic games, which are techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and programming languages (cs.PL).
